paragraphs.text: roll away your stone, i'll roll away mine. together we can see what we will find. don't leave me alone at this time, for i'm afraid of what i will discover inside.

seems that all my bridges have been burned, you say that's exactly how this grace thing works. it's not the long walk home that will change this heart, but the welcome i receive with the restart.
